<H4>3.2 Explanation of how these items might be used as a starting point for the work.</H4>

<P>With most authors of above frameworks discussions are in progress, how they might get involved. Especially those Inital EG Members or supporting the JSR wish to contribute solutions, and given some make great use of Java standards, or are considered to be used by other JSRs and implementations (e.g. Glassfish), those look especially promising. </P>

